@node BASAL "Basalt Monolith"

@{b}Basalt Monolith@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(U) / RV(U)
Type    = Artifact
Cost    = 3
Artist  = Jesper Myrfors

Text(RV): <T>: Add 3 colorless mana to your mana pool. Does not untap as
          normal during untap phase; you may spend <3> at any other time
          to untap. Drawing mana from this artifact is played as an
          interrupt.

Text(UL): <T>: Add 3 colorless mana to your mana pool. Does not untap as
          normal during untap phase; spend <3> to untap. Tapping this
          artifact can be played as an interrupt.

Text(AL): <T>: Add 3 colorless mana to your mana pool. Does not untap as
          normal during untap phase; spend <3> to untap. Tapping this
          artifact can be played as an interrupt.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_B.guide/BMONO}

