@node JUGGE "Juggernaut"

@{b}Juggernaut@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(U) / RV(U)
Type    = Artifact Creature (5/3)
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Dan Frazier

Text(RV): Must attack each turn if possible. Can't be blocked by walls.

Text(UL): Must attack each turn if possible. Can't be blocked by walls.

Flavor Text: @{i}We had taken refuge in a small cave, thinking the
             entrance was too narrow for it to follow. To our
             horror, its gigantic head smashed into the
             mountainside, ripping itself a new entrance.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_J.guide/JUGGE}

@endnode
@node LIVIN "Living Wall"

@{b}Living Wall@{ub}

Color   = Colorless
Rarity  = A/B/UL(U) / RV(U)
Type    = Artifact Creature (0/6)
Cost    = 4
Artist  = Anson Maddocks

Text(RV): Counts as a Wall.
          <1>: Regenerates

Text(UL): Counts as a Wall.
          <1>: Regenerates

Flavor Text: @{i}Some fiendish mage had created a horrifying wall of
             living flesh, patched together from a jumble of
             still-recognizable body parts. As we sought to hew
             our way through it, some unknown power healed the
             gaping wounds we cut, denying us passage.@{ui}

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_L.guide/LIWAL}

@endnode
